<div id="Scandinavian_furniture" class="Interior_Design_Options">
<img src="Scandinavian_Furniture.avif" width="500" height="263" alt="Scandinavian_furniture">
<h1 class="Image_Captions">Scandinavian furniture</h1>
<button class="Add_to_The_Preferences_List" onclick="Select_Preferences('Scandinavian_furniture')">Add to The Preferences List</button>
<button class="More_Details" onclick="display('Scandinavian_furniture');">More details</button>
<p class="Description">Scandinavian style furniture is minimalist and practical. Designers often use only solid wood to craft chair, tables, and other furniture items with a Nordic style. Natural materials like leather, linen, and Kvadrat textiles complement wood surfaces.</p>
</div>
<div id="Modern_furniture" class="Interior_Design_Options">
<img src="Modern_furniture.avif" width="500" height="263" alt="Modern_furniture">
<h1 class="Image_Captions">Modern furniture</h1>
<button class="Add_to_The_Preferences_List" onclick="Select_Preferences('Modern_furniture')">Add to The Preferences List</button>
<button class="More_Details" onclick="display('Modern_furniture');">More details</button>
<p class="Description">Modern furniture typically features simple, basic shapes like squares, rectangles, and circles. Pieces are often designed to fit together like a puzzle, making them aesthetically pleasing as well as functional.</p>
</div>
<div id="Rustic_furniture" class="Interior_Design_Options">
<img src="Rustic_Furniture.avif" width="500" height="263" alt="Rustic_furniture">
<h1 class="Image_Captions">Rustic furniture</h1>
<button class="Add_to_The_Preferences_List" onclick="Select_Preferences('Rustic_furniture')">Add to The Preferences List</button>
<button class="More_Details" onclick="display('Rustic_furniture');">More details</button>
<p class="Description">Rustic design is a style that's natural, aged, organic, and maybe even a little distressed. Design styles like farmhouse, Tuscan, or coastal can also be described as rustic. Rustic is the opposite of modern or contemporary design</p>
</div>
<h3 id="Welcome_tag"></h3>
<script>
function display(ID_Name){
if(document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("More_Details")[0].innerHTML== "More details"){
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("Description")[0].style.display="block";
document.getElementById(ID_Name).style.height="500px";
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("More_Details")[0].innerHTML="Less details";
}
else{
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("Description")[0].style.display="none";
document.getElementById(ID_Name).style.height="410px";
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("More_Details")[0].innerHTML="More details";
}
}
function Select_Preferences(ID_Name){
if(document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("Add_to_The_Preferences_List")[0].innerHTML== "Add to The Preferences List"){
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("Add_to_The_Preferences_List")[0].style.backgroundColor="green";
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("Add_to_The_Preferences_List")[0].innerHTML="Deselect the Preference";
}
else{
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("Add_to_The_Preferences_List")[0].style.backgroundColor="transparent";
document.getElementById(ID_Name).getElementsByClassName("Add_to_The_Preferences_List")[0].innerHTML="Add to The Preferences List";
}
}
document.getElementById("Welcome_tag").innerHTML="Hello "+"<%-Username%>";
function function2(){
var i;
for(i=0; i<3; i++){
	if(document.getElementsByClassName("Interior_Design_Options")[i].getElementsByClassName("Add_to_The_Preferences_List")[0].style.backgroundColor=="green"){
		document.getElementById("element_type").value=document.getElementById("element_type").value+document.getElementsByClassName("Image_Captions")[i].innerHTML+",";
	}
}
document.getElementById("my_form").submit();
}
</script>
